(98, 3, 'Audi A4', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 11px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;You are looking at a one owner, absolutely mint condition 2012 Audi A4 Quattro Prestige. This car has every option that Audi has to offer. The options include factory navigation, back up camera, parking sensors, premium sound system, upgraded wheels, heated seats, moon roof, S-Line, and much much more. You will not find a nicer A4 ANYWHERE!! All the services are totally up to date, and this car is ready to go. We do not have any commissioned sales people, we don''t play any games with you, and we will take the time to answer any questions you may have. If you are wondering why the price is so low, it is because our philosophy is to sell cars quickly and for a small profit rather than sitting on them for a long time in the hopes of making a large profit. The vast majority of our cars sell within 3 weeks from the time we get them. If this is the type of car you are looking for, please give us a call. We will be happy to answer all of your questions. We will also be happy to email you some larger, high resolution pictures of the car so that you can see the details better. We have been doing this for over 25 years. Our goal is to make each every one of our customers 100% happy with their purchase. We also pride ourselves on making the entire purchasing and shopping process enjoyable rather than stressful. We take the time to help you get the right car rather than just trying to sell you a car. Give us a chance and we think you will be glad that you did.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 11px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;br style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 11px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 11px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;* While every reasonable effort is made to ensure the acc